{"tid":573813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哲學問題- 豪宅管理員疑不滿冇得攞利是 攀上合和中心簷篷抗議","createTime":"2018-02-26T22:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T00:50:55.000Z","uid":121464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cba65a9ba8de430f40525a8675084ca2bd25025","tid":573813,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T22:56:15.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180226/57877107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57877107&d=zkf9FAfOGufQ6K%2BYQZQLXp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=74e07f57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57877107&h=d75123a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180226/57877107</a><br />\n<br />\n據了解，男子自稱為合和物業管理負責管理的樂景園屋苑職員，因不滿上司調職安排，令他在春節期間無法接觸客人，拿不到利是，而到場示威請願。<br />\n<br />\n合和實業發言人回應稱，經了解，涉事員工在由合和物業管理負責管理的樂景園屋苑工作，該員工報稱不滿年初一上班時的工作安排。據知他當日獲安排到停車場當值，但他曾稱希望到管理處當值，當時曾向上司反映不滿。<br />\n<br />\n對於有指事主不滿未能在管理處當值，以致未能向住客拜年取利是，發言人表示，一般而言，公司規定任何員工不可以主動向住客收取利是。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/065124_29978d1491d63132656ebdcd782fe6f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F065124_29978d1491d63132656ebdcd782fe6f0.png&h=b90dad25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左要利是 可以去左有幾盡<br />\n<br />\n利申 年初期間見盡茶樓阿姐同唔同保安員為左拎利是既醜惡咀臉"},{"pid":"41508dc871361f50d282c6a38bdd5f8a3b42c7a3","tid":573813,"uid":127177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T23:18:29.000Z","msg":"花紅黎架，屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406f5b167f3e5ed1e40834ff08b3ca2501de00ac","tid":573813,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T23:22:19.000Z","msg":"新年逗利是人權黎架"},{"pid":"2da8f37ee1fc167d872849cd6d1512907237b7f2","tid":573813,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b1b02173ccdb2e339bfb8cb2c8694bddd2c7c4","tid":573813,"uid":4242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:19:28.000Z","msg":"豪宅d利事分分鐘過五百一封<br />\n一日𢭃埋可能仲多過佢份底薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梗係唔gur 你啦"},{"pid":"e1ac61765ae944c0d1217d68052a46384b115e9f","tid":573813,"uid":25971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180226/57878868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57878868&d=zkf9FAfOGufQ6K%2BYQZQLXp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=72c7e5d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57878868&h=d135e770\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180226/57878868</a><br />\n<br />\n佢呢份full time 好似淨係返農歷新年嗰個月喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}